snippet.title: Plants and Politics
snippet.description:
Plants and Politics is an anti-establishment, progressive channel that offers news and commentary regarding U.S. politics as well as social, economic, and racial inequality.

And, as a certified vegan health coach, host Gina Bonanno-Lemos provides news and information about a vegan diet and how our political system affects our health. And how our food choices are affecting the planet.

Discover interviews with controversial political figures, plant-based physicians, vegan leaders, and activists. Be the first to know about new plant-based products hitting the market, and get all of the details, including ongoing updates about the domestic terrorists who attacked the United States Capitol on January 6, 2021.
